.DT
health_string
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
health_string

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
health_string -  This method returns the health string of the creature.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs string health_string(object who,
int full)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^who%^RESET%^ - the creature to get the health string for
%^BOLD%^full%^RESET%^ - whether or not to returns the full (coloured) health string
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the health string

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/health.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the health string of the creature.
It is used in extra_look in living creatures and in the 'health' command.
.EP

